node.text:
NEXT LAUNCH IS REVEALED! Did anyone guess it right?!😜🌊
Our UNDER THE SEA Collection is launching June 12th and we have so much to show youuuuu! All of the designs were inspired by the vibrant colors found in the Ocean, the glowing bioluminescent organisms, and the sand between your toes! I highly recommend watching the new campaign video because WOW it’s my favorite one to date and I’ve watched it 50x! 🥺 Plus you get to see this Aquarius one swimsuit in action! If you swipe you’ll see sneak peeks of what else is coming. ARE YOU EXCITED?! 😉👏🌊🐠

node.text:
I still remember our first date like it was yesterday. You were perfect…except for ordering a lemon drop shot (team whiskey). My awkward self went to take a sip of my drink and completely missed the straw and we both started laughing. It was right then when we both were laughing…that I knew you were about to turn my life upside down in the best way possible. I love you.😘
#AllDressedUpButHouseIsMess #OopsLol
-
PS..congrats to @kirbybetancourt on her new presets! It’s what I used to edit these photos.🤗😍
-
